      text: 'A normal App Store VPN app, a custom configuration profile, and a root certificate create very different trust boundaries. Users often treat them as interchangeable privacy tools. They are not. Profiles and certificates can change how the device handles traffic or trust in ways ordinary app permissions cannot.',
      textZh: '普通 App Store VPN、自定义配置描述文件和根证书，信任边界完全不同。用户常把它们当成可互换的隐私工具，其实不是。描述文件和证书能以普通应用权限做不到的方式改变设备处理流量或信任的方式。',
