      text: 'A well-known App Store VPN with a clear privacy policy, no demand for unrelated permissions, and no push toward installing a profile may be acceptable for travel or public Wi‑Fi. Still review the developer, recent reviews about leaks or billing, and whether the app requires an account with weak recovery options.',
      textZh: '知名 App Store VPN、隐私政策清楚、不索要无关权限、也不逼你安装描述文件时，用于旅行或公共 Wi‑Fi 可能可接受。仍要检查开发者、近期关于泄漏或扣费的评论，以及账号恢复是否脆弱。',
